# mdBook build output.
book/

# Copied-in chapters (SSOT is .omne/cfg/*.md; docs/build.{sh,ps1} regenerates
# these and prepends an AUTO-GENERATED banner at build time). Ignore every
# src/*.md, then re-include the authored pages (SUMMARY.md, introduction.md).
src/*.md
!src/SUMMARY.md
!src/introduction.md
